[14] The question must be asked: what is the significance of the Tribunal Rules in relation to the Act? It is important to consider the judgment of Jali JA in Anglo South Africa Capital (Pty) Ltd and others v Industrial Development Corporation of South Africa and another [2003] 1 CPLR 10 (CAC), where he said at 17:}
